title: Halawai Holiday Party
desc:
Aloha from Halawai! The holidays are just around the corner, and we'd like to invite you to celebrate with your NYC ohana! Join us for our final?meet up of?the year, and bring ?your friends, family, instruments, and hula hips.? There event is free, but we do ask that you RSVP! 
 See you there!
